    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
参上仕、何か御咄可<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>仕筈ニ御座候得ども、なにぶん気もちあしく、よわり居申候。然ニ佐々監察ニも申置度事も在<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>之候得バ、御ひま御座候得バ、御出可<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>被<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>下候。<lb />
いかゞ相願度。<span rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">謹言。</span>
<span rend="jisage_1" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em">廿三日<span rend="chitsuki_1" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 1em">龍</span></span>
<lb />
佐々木三四郎様<span rend="chitsuki_1" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 1em">御同宿</span>
<lb />
<span rend="jisage_1" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em">岡内俊太郎様<span rend="chitsuki_0" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 0em">楳　拝首</span></span>
<span rend="jisage_6" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 6em">左右</span>
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
